  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/9a56768119e120ce854c433bd5213af1.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/9a56768119e120ce854c433bd5213af1.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/9a56768119e120ce854c433bd5213af1.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>EXTREME EVOLUTION: Drive to Divinity</i> is an expressive platformer where every obstacle has countless, overlapping solutions.  Set free in sprawling spaces, the experiment evolves and grows.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/3ea5500d229687b88077020252c91836.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/3ea5500d229687b88077020252c91836.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/3ea5500d229687b88077020252c91836.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use § to transform between known forms at any time; invent movement combos.<br></li><li> Discover new evolutionary forms, often in temples... at greater § costs.  <br></li><li> Collect raw § to permanently increase max §.<br></li><li> Enter holes to unlock new Sites.<br></li><li> The experiment hustles, hurtles towards Earth.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/77b75ccae36da66a51ba081b4cfd8f74.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/77b75ccae36da66a51ba081b4cfd8f74.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/77b75ccae36da66a51ba081b4cfd8f74.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>String transformations together, performing extreme combos through the environment.  Take big jumps as <i>Car</i>, fling junk as <i>Pump</i>, ricochet as the bouncy <i>Bomp</i>, cling upside down as <i>Spide</i>, fling thyself as <i>Tire</i>, etc... in <i>Extreme Evolution</i>, explorative biology demands exploitation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/91f4fe0203c9588851b808770e9ef2f1.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=630 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/91f4fe0203c9588851b808770e9ef2f1.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/91f4fe0203c9588851b808770e9ef2f1.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>EEE: the Extreme Evolution Experiment. The Gods capitulate and call out, driving <i>Extreme Evolution</i>.  The nutrient rich Body, the perfect Digital Way, the abject Nothing, Infinite Spirits, Lies, and the Ouroboros: essential stopgaps along the Drive to Divinity. Inside each a Subjective! divine seal; these six seals lock away the last/first known (Human) planet (Earth).</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/55a64319a1936a36983d8359250713b6.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=630 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/55a64319a1936a36983d8359250713b6.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/55a64319a1936a36983d8359250713b6.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Movement as the original power; the ultimate story of mitochondrial evolution concludes in <i>Extreme Evolution: Drive to Divinity</i>.<br><strong><br>Photosensitivity warning: This game features many procedural visual effects & post-processing, including multi-color rapid flashing and/or strobing.  The most extreme effects can be reduced with settings in-game, but cannot be turned off fully.<br>Configure visuals with Sharp mode, Reduced Animation, and Simplified Backgrounds. </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/eb206bb60e793b0484135badbf8c31a2.poster.avif?t=1766254003\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/eb206bb60e793b0484135badbf8c31a2.webm?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111360/extras/eb206bb60e793b0484135badbf8c31a2.mp4?t=1766254003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>the 4th game by Sam Atlas<br>music by DL Salo",
